\mathrm{IE} = 13.598 + 4.478 - 2.651
\]

First, compute the difference:
\[
4.478 - 2.651 = 1.827
\]

Then add to \(\mathrm{IE_H}\):
\[
13.598 + 1.827 = 15.425
\]

